INSERT INTO `nyt_us` VALUES (1,'Friends and Family Mourn Lisa Marie Presley at Graceland','The service on Sunday, open to the public, was followed by a procession for visitors.','https://www.nytimes.com/2023/01/22/us/lisa-marie-presley-memorial.html','2023-01-22'),(2,'When Students Change Gender Identity, and Parents Don’t Know','Educators are facing wrenching new tensions over whether they should tell parents when students socially transition at school.','https://www.nytimes.com/2023/01/22/us/gender-identity-students-parents.html','2023-01-22'),(3,'Women’s March Holds Nationwide Rallies on 50th Anniversary of Roe','The annual march, which was started in 2017 as a reaction to the election of President Donald J. Trump, this year focused on abortion rights.','https://www.nytimes.com/2023/01/22/us/politics/womens-march-roe-wade.html','2023-01-23'),(4,'Florida Gives Reasons for Rejecting A.P. African American Studies Class','The state’s Department of Education cites examples of what it calls “the woke indoctrination” of students.','https://www.nytimes.com/2023/01/21/us/florida-ap-african-american-studies.html','2023-01-22'),(5,'Russian Agents Suspected of Directing Far-Right Group to Mail Bombs in Spain','U.S. officials say the operation may be a signal by Russia that the country and its proxies could carry out more terrorist actions in Europe if nations continue supporting Ukraine.','https://www.nytimes.com/2023/01/22/us/politics/russia-spain-letter-bombs.html','2023-01-22'),(6,'List of Mass Shootings in the U.S. Continues to Grow','The shooting in Monterey Park, Calif., is the deadliest in the United States since the Uvalde massacre last year.','https://www.nytimes.com/2023/01/22/us/mass-shootings-list.html','2023-01-22'),(7,'Peru’s Deadly Protests','A failed coup attempt set off unrest that has immobilized the country.','https://www.nytimes.com/2023/01/22/briefing/peru-protests.html','2023-01-22'),(8,'Inside the Hospital Where Damar Hamlin’s Life Was Saved','The trau